title: 2018 NFL Draft Rumors with Pete Prisco (Football 04/25)
description:
Pete Prisco joins Will Brinson to discuss everything he's hearing just 36 hours out from the draft, including which teams are likely to trade up into the top five or top 10, what the buzz is surrounding Lamar Jackson and if he'll be taken in the top 20 picks, whether or not we could see a deep run of offensive linemen, who the first receiver will be off the board on draft night, which pass rushers could land in the laps of teams down in the teens and much much more.
